  .bullet
    .description
      Inside your app, load up the bundled environment:
    :highlight_ruby
      require 'rubygems'
      require 'bundler/setup'

      # require your gems as usual
      require 'nokogiri'
    = link_to 'Learn More: Bundler.setup', '/v1.3/bundler_setup.html'
